nodes.bodyText:
It's simpler IMHO -- for most duties like "initTx" or "beginTx" we don't care if its eos-alpha or eos-beta. If we only keep processingMode we need to rewrite:
if (eosEnabled) {
...
}

to
if (processingMode == EXACTLY_ONCE_ALPHA || processingMode == EXACTLY_ONCE_BETA) {
...
}

what seem to be more "clumsy" ?

